---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`About · ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="关于 AIMself：产品、写作与自我进化。" />
    <style>
      .container {
        max-width: 980px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 24px;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 64px 0 28px;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: clamp(36px, 4.2vw, 54px);
        line-height: 1.06;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      }

      .lead {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.75;
        opacity: .82;
        max-width: 72ch;
      }

      .section {
        padding: 26px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.2fr .8fr;
        gap: 18px;
        align-items: start;
      }

      .card {
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.10);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 18px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
      }

      h2 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 18px;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        opacity: .80;
      }

      ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 18px;
        opacity: .80;
        line-height: 1.9;
      }

      .kicker {
        display: inline-flex;
        gap: 10px;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 6px 12px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.12);
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 12px;
        letter-spacing: .06em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        opacity: .85;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
      }

      .contact a {
        display: inline-flex;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.12);
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .muted {
        opacity: .65;
        font-size: 13px;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 860px) {
        .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="kicker">About · AIMself</div>
        <h1>关于我</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          我在这里记录从 0 到 1 的过程：产品、写作与自我进化。<br />
          目标不是“看起来努力”，而是把事情做成，并把方法沉淀下来。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="card">
            <h2>我在做什么</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>写产品笔记：需求、取舍、落地、复盘。</li>
              <li>练写作：把复杂问题讲清楚，让表达产生复利。</li>
              <li>做自我进化：用系统与习惯，减少重复试错。</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card contact">
            <h2>联系我</h2>
            <p>欢迎交流：产品 / 写作 / 方法论 / AI 工具。</p>
            <a href="mailto:dalaohuyou6@gmail.com">dalaohuyou6@gmail.com</a>
            <p class="muted">（后续你也可以在这里补充：GitHub、公众号、小红书等链接）</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>我相信什么</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>长期主义不是硬扛，而是把目标拆成可复用的日常动作。</li>
            <li>有输出的学习，才会形成自己的判断与系统。</li>
            <li>做事要“能落地”，写作要“能复用”。</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>这网站会写什么</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>产品：从想法到验证，从验证到迭代。</li>
            <li>写作：结构化表达、内容产品化、复盘模板。</li>
            <li>自我进化：习惯系统、效率方法、工具链。</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
